IMPORTANT — Third-Party Content

This software displays metadata, short quotations, and AI-generated summaries
derived from publicly available video content. All original content (speeches,
interviews, lectures, podcasts) remains the intellectual property of the
respective creators and rights holders.

Short quotations are used for educational and non-commercial purposes under
the principle of fair use / Zitatrecht (§ 51 UrhG).

Full transcripts are NOT distributed through this software.
Each entry links directly to the original source.

If you are a content creator whose work is referenced here and you would like
it removed or attributed differently, please contact:
